version_description: Sounds exactly like the studio version.
This version, is without the Capo, only chords.
Play the tab part during the intro or just strum - you can't go wrong :-).
Added capo to simplify playing, corrected chord alignment over lyrics, corrected lyrics, added missing synth section in bridge.
From Live at "Music Planet 2nite" .Acoustic, from my guitar pro tab. Live version, more complete than the other album version.
You'll need to use your thumb on the low E string for the Dm/F and D7/F# chords.
I decided to completely chord this with my own selection from what I heard. I play it arpeggiated.
